          <h6>CMMI</h6>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="tags">MI3010701</div>
                <div class="tags">3 學分</div>
                <div class="tags">第二學期</div>
                <div class="tags">大學部三、四年級</div>

              </div>
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <span>課程宗旨</span>
                <div class="line-dec"></div>
                <p>能力成熟度整合模式(Capability Maturity Model Integration, CMMI)是用於評鑑組織軟體開發流程的成熟度等級，並可用來做為軟體流程改善的標準與選擇軟體供應商的依據，目前全世界許多國家均已採用CMMI模式，我國教育部與經濟部目前也積極投入資源，協助國內軟體廠商經由導入CMMI來改善軟體開發流程，進而提升軟體品質與企業競爭力。本課程的主要目標是教導學生瞭解CMMI的精神、架構、做法與評鑑，使得學生具有規劃、執行與評估軟體流程改善的能力，以培養國內目前軟體產業急迄所需之軟體流程改善的專業人才。</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <span>課程大綱</span>
                <div class="line-dec"></div>
                <ul>
                  <li> Introduction to the Course </li>
                  <li> Process Improvement Concepts and CMMI </li>
                  <li> Overview of CMMI Model Components </li>
                  <li> Model Representations and Institutionalization </li>
                  <li> ML2 Managed Process Areas </li>
                  <li> ML3 Defined Process Areas </li>
                  <li> ML4 Quantitative Process Areas </li>
                  <li> ML5 Optimal Process Areas </li>
                  <li> Tying It All Together </li>
                  <li> CMMI Maturity Profile and Performance Results </li>
                  <li> CMMI Appraisals - ARC & SCAMPI </li>
                  <li> CMMI Adoptions in Taiwan </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
